#: .\CDDAXP_Archery.json
msgid "shuriken"
msgid_plural "shurikens"
msgstr[0] "手里剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shuriken', 'str_pl': 'shurikens'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Archery.json
msgid ""
"A thin and flat knife made for throwing, shaped like a star.  Its "
"ineffective cutting edge and odd shape makes it unsuitable for use as a "
"tool."
msgstr "一种专为投掷设计的薄而平的刀，形状如星。其低效的切割刃和奇特形状使其不适合作为工具使用。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Archery.json
msgid "diamond shuriken"
msgid_plural "diamond shurikens"
msgstr[0] "金刚石手里剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'diamond shuriken', 'str_pl': 'diamond
#. shurikens'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Archery.json
msgid ""
"This throwing star has been enhanced with a coating of diamond-like carbon, "
"making it far more deadly."
msgstr "这枚手里剑经过类金刚石碳涂层强化，使其致命性大幅提升。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Archery.json
msgid "ceramic shuriken"
msgid_plural "ceramic shurikens"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷手里剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic shuriken', 'str_pl': 'ceramic
#. shurikens'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Archery.json
msgid ""
"This throwing star is made out of very hard and tough hi-tech ceramic, "
"making it far more deadly."
msgstr "这枚手里剑由坚硬且坚韧的高科技陶瓷制成，使其致命性大幅提升。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "Miltech enviromask"
msgid_plural "Miltech enviromasks"
msgstr[0] "Miltech环境防护面罩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Miltech enviromask'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A Miltech lightweight protection mask with high efficiency multipurpose "
"filters, that straps over mouth and nose only.  Provides very good "
"environmental protection from smoke and other contaminants."
msgstr "一款Miltech轻量化防护面罩，配备高效多用途过滤器，仅覆盖口鼻。能提供出色的环境防护，抵御烟雾及其他污染物。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "rioter trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "rioter trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "防暴风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rioter trenchcoat'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift armoured cotton trenchcoat that leaves your arms unencumbered.  "
"Has plenty of storage space due to its many pockets."
msgstr "一件临时制作的装甲棉质风衣，让你的手臂活动自如。因其多个口袋而拥有充足的存储空间。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "rioter pants"
msgid_plural "rioter pantss"
msgstr[0] "防暴裤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rioter pants'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift armoured pair of pants lined with pockets, offering lots of "
"storage."
msgstr "一条临时制作的装甲裤，内衬多个口袋，提供大量存储空间。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "razor edge throwing shield"
msgid_plural "razor edge throwing shields"
msgstr[0] "利刃投掷盾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'razor edge throwing shield'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"An heavy reshaped manhole cover, lightened and reforged as the throwing "
"shield of the Captain.  Now you need only a flying Power Armor..."
msgstr "一个经过重塑的厚重井盖，经过轻量化处理和重铸，成为队长的投掷盾。现在你只需要一套飞行动力装甲……"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "survivor rioter trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "survivor rioter trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "幸存者暴动风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor rioter trenchcoat'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift armoured cotton trenchcoat with pouches, that leaves your arms "
"unencumbered.  It is also combined with a big leather back holster.  "
"Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "一件临时制作的装甲棉质风衣，带有多个口袋，确保手臂活动自如。它还结合了一个大型皮革背枪套。激活以收枪/拔枪。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "survivor rioter pants"
msgid_plural "survivor rioter pantss"
msgstr[0] "幸存者暴动裤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor rioter pants'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift armoured pair of pants lined with pockets, combined with a "
"multipurpose bandolier as belt."
msgstr "一条临时制作的装甲裤，内衬多个口袋，并配有一条多功能子弹带作为腰带。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "bracer"
msgid_plural "bracers"
msgstr[0] "护臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bracer', 'str_pl': 'bracers'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "A metal arm-guard that protect the forearm against injury."
msgstr "一种金属护臂，用于保护前臂免受伤害。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "RILLE pack"
msgid_plural "RILLE packs"
msgstr[0] "RILLE背包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'RILLE pack'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"The 'RIoter Lightweight Load-carrying Equipment' is an advanced military "
"backpack heavily customized.  Armoured and covered with pockets, it uses two"
" granade bandoliers as shoulder straps."
msgstr "'暴动者轻量负载装备'是一款经过高度定制的先进军用背包。装甲覆盖并配有多个口袋，使用两条手榴弹带作为肩带。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "lamellar chitinous trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "lamellar chitinous trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "层状几丁质风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lamellar chitinous trenchcoat'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift armoured cotton trenchcoat with pouches, padded in kevlar and "
"chitin.  It has a nasty entomologic look and it is also combined with a big "
"leather back holster.  Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "一件临时制作的装甲棉质风衣，带有多个口袋，内衬凯夫拉和几丁质。它具有令人不适的昆虫学外观，并配有一个大型皮革背枪套。激活以收枪/拔枪。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "lamellar chitinous pants"
msgid_plural "lamellar chitinous pantss"
msgstr[0] "层状几丁质裤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lamellar chitinous pants'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift armoured pair of pants padded in kevlar and chitin, combined "
"with a multipurpose bandolier as belt.  It has a nasty entomologic look."
msgstr "一条临时制作的装甲裤，内衬凯夫拉和几丁质，并配有一条多功能子弹带作为腰带。它具有令人不适的昆虫学外观。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "rioter long-sleeved shirt"
msgid_plural "rioter long-sleeved shirts"
msgstr[0] "暴动者长袖衬衫"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'rioter long-sleeved shirt'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'chitinous rioter shirt'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'bony rioter shirt'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'ceramic rioter shirt'}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "You stash your %s."
msgstr "你藏起了你的%s。"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'rioter long-sleeved shirt'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'chitinous rioter shirt'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'bony rioter shirt'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'ceramic rioter shirt'}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "Stash ammo"
msgstr "藏匿弹药"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rioter long-sleeved shirt'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built long-sleeved shirt covered in pouches with two ammo satchels "
"to hold magazines close at hand.  Durable and carefully crafted to be "
"comfortable to wear.  Activate to stash/draw magazines."
msgstr "一件定制长袖衬衫，覆盖多个口袋，并配有两个弹药包，方便随时取用弹匣。耐用且精心制作，穿着舒适。激活以存放/取出弹匣。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "chitinous rioter shirt"
msgid_plural "chitinous rioter shirts"
msgstr[0] "几丁质暴动衬衫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chitinous rioter shirt'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built rigid version of the standard rioter shirt, padded in kevlar "
"and chitin.  Durable and carefully crafted to be comfortable to wear.  "
"Activate to stash/draw up to two magazines."
msgstr "标准暴动衬衫的定制硬化版本，内衬凯夫拉和几丁质。耐用且精心制作，穿着舒适。激活以存放/取出最多两个弹匣。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "bony rioter shirt"
msgid_plural "bony rioter shirts"
msgstr[0] "骨质暴动衬衫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bony rioter shirt'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built rigid version of the standard rioter shirt, padded in kevlar "
"and bones.  Durable and carefully crafted to be comfortable to wear.  "
"Activate to stash/draw up to two magazines."
msgstr "标准暴动衬衫的定制硬化版本，内衬凯夫拉和骨骼。耐用且精心制作，穿着舒适。激活以存放/取出最多两个弹匣。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "ceramic rioter shirt"
msgid_plural "ceramic rioter shirts"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷暴动衬衫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic rioter shirt'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built rigid version of the standard rioter shirt, padded in kevlar "
"and ceramic.  Durable and carefully crafted to be comfortable to wear.  "
"Activate to stash/draw up to two magazines."
msgstr "标准暴动衬衫的定制硬化版本，内衬凯夫拉和陶瓷。耐用且精心制作，穿着舒适。激活以存放/取出最多两个弹匣。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "lamellar bony trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "lamellar bony trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "层状骨质风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lamellar bony trenchcoat'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift armoured cotton trenchcoat with pouches, padded in kevlar and "
"bones.  It has a creepy look and it is also combined with a big leather back"
" holster.  Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "一件临时制作的装甲棉质风衣，带有多个口袋，内衬凯夫拉和骨骼。它具有令人毛骨悚然的外观，并配有一个大型皮革背枪套。激活以收枪/拔枪。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "lamellar bony pants"
msgid_plural "lamellar bony pantss"
msgstr[0] "层状骨质裤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lamellar bony pants'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift armoured pair of pants padded in kevlar and bones, combined with"
" a multipurpose bandolier as belt.  It has a creepy look."
msgstr "一条临时制作的装甲裤，内衬凯夫拉和骨骼，并配有一条多功能子弹带作为腰带。它具有令人毛骨悚然的外观。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "lamellar ceramic trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "lamellar ceramic trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "层状陶瓷风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lamellar ceramic trenchcoat'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift armoured cotton trenchcoat with pouches, padded in kevlar and "
"ceramic.  It has an hi-tech look and it is also combined with a big leather "
"back holster.  Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "一件临时制作的装甲棉质风衣，带有多个口袋，内衬凯夫拉和陶瓷。它具有高科技外观，并配有一个大型皮革背枪套。激活以收枪/拔枪。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "lamellar ceramic pants"
msgid_plural "lamellar ceramic pantss"
msgstr[0] "层状陶瓷裤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lamellar ceramic pants'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift armoured pair of pants padded in kevlar and ceramic, combined "
"with a multipurpose bandolier as belt.  It has an hi-tech look."
msgstr "一条临时制作的装甲裤，内衬凯夫拉和陶瓷，配有多功能子弹带作为腰带。外观颇具高科技感。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "heavy lamellar trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "heavy lamellar trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "重型鳞甲风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy lamellar trenchcoat'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift heavy armoured cotton trenchcoat with pouches, padded in kevlar "
"and steel.  It has a bulletproof look and it is also combined with a big "
"fast leather back holster.  Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "一件临时制作的重型装甲棉风衣，带有口袋，内衬凯夫拉和钢板。外观防弹，并配有一个大型快速皮革背枪套。激活以收枪/拔枪。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "heavy lamellar pants"
msgid_plural "heavy lamellar pantss"
msgstr[0] "重型鳞甲裤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy lamellar pants'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift heavy armoured pair of pants padded in kevlar and steel, "
"combined with a multipurpose bandolier as belt.  It has a bulletproof look."
msgstr "一条临时制作的重型装甲裤，内衬凯夫拉和钢板，配有多功能子弹带作为腰带。外观防弹。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "fast back holster"
msgid_plural "fast back holsters"
msgstr[0] "快速背枪套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fast back holster'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A leather holster, big enough for a rifle or other large gun.  Designed to "
"be strapped to the back.  It is engineered with a mechanism specific for "
"fast draw.  Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "一个皮革枪套，大小足以容纳步枪或其他大型枪支。设计用于背带。采用快速拔枪专用机械结构。激活以收枪/拔枪。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "bulletproof lamellar trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "bulletproof lamellar trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "防弹鳞甲风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bulletproof lamellar trenchcoat'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift bulletproof cotton trenchcoat with pouches, padded in superalloy"
" and steel.  It has a bulky look and it is also combined with a big fast "
"leather back holster.  Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "一件临时制作的防弹棉风衣，带有口袋，内衬超级合金和钢板。外观厚重，并配有一个大型快速皮革背枪套。激活以收枪/拔枪。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid "bulletproof lamellar pants"
msgid_plural "bulletproof lamellar pantss"
msgstr[0] "防弹鳞甲裤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bulletproof lamellar pants'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift bulletproof pair of pants padded in superalloy and steel, "
"combined with a multipurpose bandolier as belt.  It has a bulky look."
msgstr "一条临时制作的防弹裤，内衬超级合金和钢板，配有多功能子弹带作为腰带。外观厚重。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Comestibles.json
msgid "anabolic steroid"
msgid_plural "anabolic steroids"
msgstr[0] "合成代谢类固醇"

#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str': 'anabolic steroid', 'str_pl':
#. 'anabolic steroids'}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Comestibles.json
msgid "You shoot up."
msgstr "你注射了它。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'anabolic steroid', 'str_pl': 'anabolic
#. steroids'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Comestibles.json
msgid ""
"The proper term for this compound is anabolic-androgenic steroid and it is a"
" synthetic variations of the male sex hormone testosterone.  You need a "
"syringe to inject it."
msgstr "这种化合物的正确名称是合成代谢雄性类固醇，是男性性激素睾酮的合成变体。你需要注射器来注射它。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Comestibles.json
msgid "meal replacement hyperproteic bar"
msgid_plural "meal replacement hyperproteic bars"
msgstr[0] "代餐高蛋白棒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'meal replacement hyperproteic bar', 'str_pl':
#. 'meal replacement hyperproteic bars'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A tasty and nutritious mixture of proteins and vitamins compressed in a bar "
"that can replace a complete meal.  An healthy bomb of energy!"
msgstr "一种美味且营养丰富的蛋白质和维生素混合物，压缩成棒状，可替代完整的一餐。健康的能量炸弹！"

#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid "Augmented Reality - LOW"
msgstr "增强现实 - 低"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Augmented Reality - LOW'.
#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid ""
"Augmented Reality - LOW: A green grid helps to correctly evaluate heights "
"and distances."
msgstr "增强现实 - 低：绿色网格有助于准确评估高度和距离。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid "Augmented Reality - MEDIUM"
msgstr "增强现实 - 中"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Augmented Reality - MEDIUM'.
#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid ""
"Augmented Reality - MEDIUM: Objects and creatures are highlited on the grid."
msgstr "增强现实 - 中：物体和生物在网格上高亮显示。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid "Augmented Reality - HIGH"
msgstr "增强现实 - 高"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Augmented Reality - HIGH'.
#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid ""
"Augmented Reality - HIGH: 'ID' for objects and creatures are shown, with "
"other informations and biometrical data."
msgstr "增强现实 - 高：显示物体和生物的“ID”，以及其他信息和生物特征数据。"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Augmented Reality - LOW, Augmented Reality
#. - MEDIUM, Augmented Reality - HIGH'.
#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid "'Augmented Reality' is switched off."
msgstr "“增强现实”已关闭。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid "Anabolic comedown"
msgstr "类固醇药效消退"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Anabolic comedown'.
#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid "GHWAAA!  Me sss...  Sputi...  STUPID!"
msgstr "嘎啊啊！我... 吐... 蠢货！"

#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid "Roid on steroids"
msgstr "类固醇狂暴"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Roid on steroids'.
#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid "Feel the roid rage!!!"
msgstr "感受类固醇的狂怒！！！"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Anabolic comedown, Roid on steroids'.
#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid "Steroid effect vanish."
msgstr "类固醇效果消失。"

