msgstr "破碎"

#: .\CDDAXP_Melee.json
msgid "bo"
msgid_plural "bos"
msgstr[0] "棍"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bo'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Melee.json
msgid ""
"The bo is a very tall and long staff weapon usually made with hard or "
"flexible wood, used in Okinawa and feudal Japan."
msgstr "棒是一种非常高大且长的杖类武器，通常由硬木或柔韧木材制成，在冲绳和封建时代的日本使用。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Melee.json
msgid "nunchaku"
msgid_plural "nunchakus"
msgstr[0] "双节棍"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nunchaku'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Melee.json
msgid ""
"The nunchaku is a traditional okinawan martial arts weapon consisting of two"
" sticks connected at one end by a short chain or rope."
msgstr "双节棍是一种传统的冲绳武术武器，由两根棍子在一端通过短链或绳索连接而成。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Melee.json
msgid "sai"
msgid_plural "sais"
msgstr[0] "十手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sai'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Melee.json
msgid ""
"The basic form of the sai is that of a pointed, prong shaped metal baton, "
"with two curved prongs projecting from the handle.  It's like a skewer and "
"you can also cook with it."
msgstr "十手的基本形态是一种尖头、叉形的金属短棍，手柄处伸出两根弯曲的叉齿。它像一根烤肉叉，你也可以用它来烹饪。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Heavy Assault Marine"
msgstr "重装突击陆战队员"

#: .\CDDAXP_Professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Heavy Assault Marine"
msgstr "重装突击陆战队员"

#. ~ Profession (male Heavy Assault Marine) description
#: .\CDDAXP_Professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are an armoured badass unstoppable soldier with a nasty big fucking gun,"
" but also a lone survivor with no support or resupply...  Don't waste your "
"firepower!"
msgstr "你是一名身披重甲、势不可挡的狠角色士兵，手持一把又大又猛的枪，但也是一个没有支援或补给的孤独幸存者……别浪费你的火力！"

#. ~ Profession (female Heavy Assault Marine) description
#: .\CDDAXP_Professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are an armoured badass unstoppable soldier with a nasty big fucking gun,"
" but also a lone survivor with no support or resupply...  Don't waste your "
"firepower!"
