msgid "You need a source of fire!"
msgstr "你需要火源！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'happo', 'str_pl': 'happos'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"A small eggshell filled with ignitable smoking powder generally used to "
"facilitate escape.  Use this item to light the fuse.  You will, of course, "
"need a lighter or matches in your inventory to do this."
msgstr "一个装满可燃烟雾粉末的小蛋壳，通常用于辅助逃脱。使用此物品点燃引信。当然，你需要背包里有打火机或火柴才能做到。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "lit happo"
msgid_plural "lit happos"
msgstr[0] "点燃的happo"

#. ~ Use action no_deactivate_msg for {'str': 'lit happo', 'str_pl': 'lit
#. happos'}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "You've already lit the %s, try throwing it instead."
msgstr "你已经点燃了%s，试试把它扔出去吧。"

#. ~ Use action sound_msg for {'str': 'lit happo', 'str_pl': 'lit happos'}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ssss..."
msgstr "嘶嘶……"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lit happo', 'str_pl': 'lit happos'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "The fuse on this happo is lit and hissing."
msgstr "这个happo的引信已点燃，正发出嘶嘶声。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "Miltech 'AR' projector"
msgid_plural "Miltech 'AR' projectors"
msgstr[0] "Miltech 'AR'投影仪"

#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str': "Miltech 'AR' projector"}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "You push activation button.  'AR' enhance your surroundings."
msgstr "你按下启动按钮。'AR'增强了你的周围环境。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Miltech 'AR' projector"}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"A little laser projector of 'Augmented Reality', by Miltech.  When loaded, "
"activate it up to three times to enhance your surroundings for a short "
"period of time."
msgstr "Miltech制造的'增强现实'小型激光投影仪。装载后，最多可激活三次，在短时间内增强你的周围环境。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "AppleSoft portable personal assistant"
msgid_plural "AppleSoft portable personal assistants"
msgstr[0] "AppleSoft便携式个人助理"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'AppleSoft portable personal assistant'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'AppleSoft portable personal assistant (on)'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"An AppleSoft portable personal assistant in the form of a tablet PC.  The "
"connection thing is useless, but 'Sirana' (the device 'AI') and his internal"
" multipurpose database can still help you.  Runs on conventional batteries."
msgstr ""
"一款平板电脑形式的AppleSoft便携式个人助理。连接功能已无用，但'Sirana'（设备'AI'）及其内部多功能数据库仍能帮助你。使用常规电池运行。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "AppleSoft portable personal assistant (on)"
msgid_plural "AppleSoft portable personal assistant (on)s"
msgstr[0] "AppleSoft便携式个人助理（开启）"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "screaming bomb"
msgid_plural "screaming bombs"
msgstr[0] "尖叫炸弹"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'screaming bomb', 'str_pl': 'screaming
#. bombs'}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "The bomb say:  'Beware!  I LIVE!!!'."
msgstr "炸弹说道：'小心！我还活着！！！'。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'screaming bomb', 'str_pl': 'screaming bombs'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"This WAS a talking doll, but now it is a screaming...  Well...  BOMB!  The "
"grin on its face is insane.  The Joker would be proud of you!  Use this item"
" to activate the timer."
msgstr "这曾是一个会说话的玩偶，但现在它是一个尖叫的……嗯……炸弹！它脸上的笑容疯狂至极。小丑都会为你感到骄傲！使用此物品激活定时器。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "'alive' screaming bomb"
msgid_plural "'alive' screaming bombs"
msgstr[0] "'活着的'尖叫炸弹"

#. ~ Use action no_deactivate_msg for {'str': "'alive' screaming bomb",
#. 'str_pl': "'alive' screaming bombs"}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "The bomb say:  'Throw me, STUPID!!!'."
msgstr "炸弹说道：'扔我啊，笨蛋！！！'。"

#. ~ Use action sound_msg for {'str': "'alive' screaming bomb", 'str_pl':
#. "'alive' screaming bombs"}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "Tic-toc!  HUG-MEEE!  AHAHAH!!!"
msgstr "滴答！抱抱我！啊哈哈哈！！！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "'alive' screaming bomb", 'str_pl': "'alive'
#. screaming bombs"}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "The screaming bomb is 'alive'.  It'll explode any moment now."
msgstr "尖叫炸弹'活着'。它随时都可能爆炸。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "interior atomic lamp"
msgid_plural "interior atomic lamps"
msgstr[0] "室内原子灯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'interior atomic lamp'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"Enjoy the perpetual solar-like light of this custom made atomic interior "
"lamp and feel confident that you won't have to worry about depleting its "
"power supply for at least 40 million years of faithful service."
msgstr "享受这款定制原子室内灯永恒的类日光照明，并确信至少在4000万年的忠实服务中，你无需担心其电源耗尽。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "vacuum-packed turning meat slice"
msgid_plural "vacuum-packed turning meat slices"
msgstr[0] "真空包装的转化肉片"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'vacuum-packed turning meat slice', 'str_pl':
#. 'vacuum-packed turning meat slices'}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "You inspect and shake the bag.  The meat is ready."
msgstr "你检查并摇晃袋子。肉已准备就绪。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'vacuum-packed turning meat slice',
#. 'str_pl': 'vacuum-packed turning meat slices'}.
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "You must wait.  The turning meat isn't done yet."
msgstr "你必须等待。转化肉尚未完成。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vacuum-packed turning meat slice', 'str_pl':
#. 'vacuum-packed turning meat slices'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"This is a bag of vacuum packed tainted meat which is undergoing a strange "
"chemical processes that will make it edible again.  A dezombification "
"remedy?  Sadly, this is true only for slices of meat...  Activate it when it"
" is done."
msgstr "这是一袋真空包装的污染肉片，正在经历奇怪的化学过程，使其再次可食用。一种去僵尸化疗法？遗憾的是，这仅适用于肉片……完成后激活它。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ceramic katana"
msgid_plural "ceramic katanas"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷武士刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic katana'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"The blade of this katana is made out of very hard and tough hi-tech ceramic."
"  It is now light, stronger and sharper than Muramasa could have ever "
"dreamed."
msgstr "这把武士刀的刀刃由非常坚硬坚韧的高科技陶瓷制成。它现在轻便、坚固且锋利，远超村正所能想象。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ceramic machete"
msgid_plural "ceramic machetes"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷砍刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic machete'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"Wickedly sharp, light and nearly indestructible, this machete cleaves "
"vegetation and the living dead with equal ease."
msgstr "这把砍刀锋利无比、轻便且几乎坚不可摧，无论是劈砍植被还是对付活死人，都同样轻松自如。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ceramic knife"
msgid_plural "ceramic knives"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷战斗刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic knife', 'str_pl': 'ceramic knives'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"The blade of this combat knife is made out of very hard, light and tough hi-"
"tech ceramic."
msgstr "这把战斗刀的刀刃由非常坚硬、轻便且坚韧的高科技陶瓷制成。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ceramic kukri"
msgid_plural "ceramic kukris"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷廓尔喀弯刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic kukri'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"A kukri with a synthetic ceramic blade.  Extremely light, durable and "
"sharper than any steel blade, this is a fearsome weapon."
msgstr "一把采用合成陶瓷刀刃的廓尔喀弯刀。极其轻便、耐用，且比任何钢刃都更锋利，这是一件令人畏惧的武器。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ceramic rapier"
msgid_plural "ceramic rapiers"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷刺剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic rapier'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"The blade of this rapier is made out of very hard, light and tough hi-tech "
"ceramic, rendering it far more deadly."
msgstr "这把刺剑的刀刃由非常坚硬、轻便且坚韧的高科技陶瓷制成，使其致命性大幅提升。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ceramic broadsword"
msgid_plural "ceramic broadswords"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷阔剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic broadsword'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"The blade of this broadsword is a very hard, light and razor-sharp piece of "
"hi-tech ceramic, making you the deadliest knight in the realm.  Your "
"blademaster would be proud."
msgstr "这把阔剑的刀刃是一块非常坚硬、轻便且锋利如剃刀的高科技陶瓷，让你成为王国中最致命的骑士。你的剑术大师会为此感到骄傲。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ceramic zweihÃ¤nder"
msgid_plural "ceramic zweihÃ¤nders"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷双手剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic zweihÃ¤nder'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"This zweihander's blade is a very hard, light and razor-sharp piece of hi-"
"tech ceramic, making it pack even more of a punch."
msgstr "这把双手剑的刀刃是一块非常坚硬、轻便且锋利如剃刀的高科技陶瓷，使其威力更加强大。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ceramic wakizashi"
msgid_plural "ceramic wakizashis"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷胁差"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic wakizashi'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"This wakizashi's blade is a very hard, light and razor-sharp piece of hi-"
"tech ceramic, making it as strong as, well, hi-tech ceramic..."
msgstr "这把胁差的刀刃是一块非常坚硬、轻便且锋利如剃刀的高科技陶瓷，使其坚固程度如同……嗯，高科技陶瓷本身……"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ceramic nodachi"
msgid_plural "ceramic nodachis"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷野太刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic nodachi'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"This nodachi's massive blade has been shaped with hi-tech ceramic, making it"
" far more deadly."
msgstr "这把野太刀的巨型刀刃由高科技陶瓷塑形而成，使其致命性大幅提升。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "diamond kusarigama"
msgid_plural "diamond kusarigamas"
msgstr[0] "钻石锁镰"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'diamond kusarigama'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"The edge of this kusarigama's blade has been enhanced with a coating of "
"diamond-like carbon, making it far more deadly."
msgstr "这把锁镰的刀刃边缘通过类金刚石碳涂层增强，使其致命性大幅提升。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid "ceramic kusarigama"
msgid_plural "ceramic kusarigamas"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷锁镰"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic kusarigama'}
#: .\CDDAXP_Tools.json
msgid ""
"This kusarigama is made out of very hard and tough hi-tech ceramic, making "
"it far more deadly."
msgstr "这把锁镰由非常坚硬且坚韧的高科技陶瓷制成，使其致命性大幅提升。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Underbarrel.json
msgid "ceramic bayonet"
msgid_plural "ceramic bayonets"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷刺刀"

#: .\CDDAXP_Underbarrel.json
msgid ""
"This bayonet is made with a very hard, light and razor-sharp piece of hi-"
