msgid "ceramic sword bayonet"
msgid_plural "ceramic sword bayonets"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷剑式刺刀"

#: .\CDDAXP_Underbarrel.json
msgid ""
"This sword bayonet is made with a very hard, light and razor-sharp piece of "
"hi-tech ceramic, greatly augmenting its cutting damage."
msgstr "这把剑式刺刀采用一块非常坚硬、轻便且锋利如剃刀的高科技陶瓷制成，极大地增强了其切割伤害。"

#: .\CDDAXP_Underbarrel.json
msgid "ceramic pistol bayonet"
msgid_plural "ceramic pistol bayonets"
msgstr[0] "陶瓷手枪刺刀"

#: .\CDDAXP_Underbarrel.json
msgid ""
"This pistol bayonet is made with a very hard, light and razor-sharp piece of"
